{"tid":2152790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藍絲棄大叠《蘋果》街坊拾回","createTime":"2020-08-12T07:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T08:08:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"49197222516564852be6c584bf5bbad1b61ef9ef","tid":2152790,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:42:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/OY4U5TBRX4OCPL7SH5ZUFHOKUQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FOY4U5TBRX4OCPL7SH5ZUFHOKUQ%2F&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWfyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=04bf1422\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FOY4U5TBRX4OCPL7SH5ZUFHOKUQ%2F&h=4e27f11c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/OY4U5TBRX4OCPL7SH5ZUFHOKUQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n藍絲棄大叠《蘋果》街坊拾回<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】有網上流傳短片，一名男子疑取走多份《蘋果日報》，然後將報紙丟進回收箱。及後有善心人從回收箱內取回《蘋果》，並批評藍絲行為自私和不智。<br />\n<br />\n網上片段所見，事發地點在上水新都廣場對開。一名男子將大叠《蘋果日報》丟進一個回收箱內。拍片者看不過眼，上前質問對方：「你又唔係睇，又要丟晒啲嘢（《蘋果日報》），。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RRRWlZoR-krySe84AaPtgvSEyaQ=/1151x902/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7RDR7DAREBVFZJ5XVCTBYSZAB4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRRRWlZoR-krySe84AaPtgvSEyaQ%3D%2F1151x902%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7RDR7DAREBVFZJ5XVCTBYSZAB4.gif&h=861b93a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有藍絲將多份《蘋果日報》丟進回收箱。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥行為自私<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：篩選傳媒被轟 警：會優化<br />\n<br />\n記者其後在上水現場了解，有街坊稱，有善心人從回收箱內，把被丟棄的《蘋果》拿出，再放在回收箱頂，其後所有《蘋果》被途人逐一取走。<br />\n<br />\n有上水街坊對蘋果日報大樓遭香港國安人員高調入內搜查，感到痛心，「始終香。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n街坊林先生亦批評該男子行為自私，「如果係佢買都OK嘅，可能佢都想支持，。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"527f96ef345bf89a1615fc56d571947f60a82c72","tid":2152790,"uid":282490,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:45:35.000Z","msg":"下次見藍絲報紙都應該拎多啲<br />\n轉頭拎去回收箱"},{"pid":"0b1fe3e91ffdc0210eca523eed2fcfffa5dd8036","tid":2152790,"uid":180124,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:47:31.000Z","msg":"公道講句，其實大家買咁多都係睇唔哂架啦<br />\n最後都係浪費左"},{"pid":"67133ba7cb52c8cc28b69570b43dedf07a693223","tid":2152790,"uid":102681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b1fe3e91ffdc0210eca523eed2fcfffa5dd8036","tid":2152790,"uid":180124,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:47:31.000Z","msg":"公道講句，其實大家買咁多都係睇唔哂架啦<br />\n最後都係浪費左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:49:40.000Z","msg":"咁所以咪派畀人，物盡其用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7383dbe4903f73f42c82363aa1a9ce5abb6a667","tid":2152790,"uid":252877,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:50:55.000Z","msg":"咁撚似鄧小強嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155cf5b5235cb42a6a9188e2af844e219f03c022","tid":2152790,"uid":180124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"67133ba7cb52c8cc28b69570b43dedf07a693223","tid":2152790,"uid":102681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b1fe3e91ffdc0210eca523eed2fcfffa5dd8036","tid":2152790,"uid":180124,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:47:31.000Z","msg":"公道講句，其實大家買咁多都係睇唔哂架啦<br />\n最後都係浪費左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:49:40.000Z","msg":"咁所以咪派畀人，物盡其用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:55:11.000Z","msg":"大家都買左自己果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3dd16fac1a5dcb54c96c8d76eef6d6280646b22","tid":2152790,"uid":128369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b7383dbe4903f73f42c82363aa1a9ce5abb6a667","tid":2152790,"uid":252877,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:50:55.000Z","ms